Get started with a completely redesigned training experience! Our activity library with 5000+ activities got a facelift and we are proud of the result.
- Two new viewing modes for your training: A simple, default mode and an advanced mode for extra convenience
- Share your training summary and show off your progress!
- Swipe planned activities to mark them as done or to select them
- A brand-new, easy to use, activity editor
- The redesigned player also has improved audio feedback
- User Experience improvements and bugfixes
